node.text: President Biden struggled to speak to a half-empty auditorium during a recent town hall. When he wasn’t mixing up his words, Biden was lying to the crowd. TONIGHT on “Hannity,” we’ll show you clips of Biden’s worst moments and bring you reactions from Rep. Ronny Jackson and Stephen Miller. Tune in at 9 PM ET or set your DVR to never miss an episode!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sean Hannity on July 22, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'PSAKI DEFENDS HUNTER BIDEN MEETING POTENTIAL ART BUYERS Photo Brochstein/S 出 Hannity'.

node.text: White House Press Secretary Jen Psaki defended Hunter Biden’s appearance at two art shows where potential buyers will be present. She justified Hunter’s presence by emphasizing that the gallerist would discuss sales with buyers. Does she really expect the American people to believe that he won’t talk to anyone about sales?! Miranda Devine and John Solomon will discuss the Biden family’s corruption and Hunter's “art” TONIGHT on “Hannity.”

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sean Hannity on July 22, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and text that says 'ONE-ON-ONE WITH MARK LEVIN TUNE INTO Hannity TONIGHT 9PM ET'.

node.text: “The Great One,” Mark Levin will join “Hannity” to discuss the Biden administration’s decision to put sanctions on Cuba amid the historic protests. Interesting timing! Tune in at 9 PM ET or set your DVR for this must-see interview!
Sen. Marco Rubio explains how Cuba's regime has failed its country and why he thinks the people of Cuba know how to fix it.

node.text: FL Gov. Ron DeSantis and Sen. Marco Rubio will join “Hannity,” TONIGHT for an exciting town hall where they will discuss the Cuban people’s fight for democracy. Tune in at 9 PM ET or set your DVR for this must-see episode!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sean Hannity on July 21, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and text.

node.text: Floridians are gathering together in support of their friends and families in Cuba, who are fighting for their freedom. TONIGHT on “Hannity,” we will discuss the situation in Cuba and give you LIVE reactions from Gov. Ron DeSantis and Sen. Marco Rubio. Tune in at 9 PM ET or set your DVR to never miss an episode!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sean Hannity on July 21, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Hannity LIVE FROM OM MIAMI TUNE IN TONIGHT 9PM ET VFX FOX NEWS channel'.

node.text: TONIGHT, we’ll cover the crisis in Cuba and the people’s fight for freedom LIVE from Miami, Florida. You don’t want to miss our amazing lineup, including Gov. Ron DeSantis and Sen. Marco Rubio! Tune in at 9 PM ET or set your DVR for this can’t-miss town hall!
